This practical is based on Fuzzy Set Theory.

In normal sets:

An element either belongs or does not belong.
Membership is only:
0 or 1

But in fuzzy sets:

Elements can belong partially.
Membership values range between:
0 to 1

Example:

Tall people = {Ayesha/0.7, Rahul/0.5}

Meaning:

Ayesha is tall with degree 0.7
Rahul is tall with degree 0.5







